# Changelog
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [Unreleased]

## [0.1.2] - 2022-01-13
### Changed
- Calendar title updated with cook type

### Fixed
- Recipe ingredents must be in same measurement (fixed resipes.json - need to fix function)

## [0.1.1] - 2022-01-12
### Added
- Set plan start date
- Google calendar authentication
- Add plan to google calendar 

## [0.1.0] - 2022-01-12
### Added
- Function to read saved config file.
- getPlan basic structure
- Load recipes file
- option to download recipes is none exists
- test recipes for download
- added requirements.txt
- Random select meal
- Generate grocery list based on selected meal plan 

### Changed
- Logging variable changes based on arguments

## [0.0.2] - 2022-01-09
### Added
- Logging using python logging

### Changed
- Default config file changes

## [0.0.1] - 2022-01-08
### Added
- This CHANGELOG based on the standard from https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/
- README about the project description and goals
- LICENSE - MIT
- MealPlanner.py inital structure and plan
- Added TODO list